script = ExtResource("1_m1mx8")
release_version = "v1.3.0 (CM37E)"
notes = "Hey! This is the initial release of the modfork, so I thought I might as well make a series of patch notes. This fork is meant to be a completed version of the game, as it was left a bit unfinished.
[TITLE]Mods added
A lot of mods were added, which gave the following effects:
  The Haunted Cog Golf Course's fog is now decreased
  The Battle UI has been slightly adjusted
  Health lights have been changed
  Cog Creator Plus implemented. Now you can tweak a lot more, including a groovy new way to turn off cog suits for 2D and 3D non-cog cogs!
  Endless implemented. Enjoy the game forever!
  Play Dead no longer takes forever
  You can now restart the floor without losing your save if you die
  Mole Stomp has been reworked. You can now stomp on Yellow Moles! Scores and Red Moles were adjusted to compensate.
[TITLE] Exclusive Additions
Added 2 new characters: Franz Neckvein and Bumpy Bumblebehr
Added a new facility: The Frozen D.A. Office
The Faulty Factory and Haunted Cog Golf Course now have different icons. They also have edited versions of their respective normal facilitie's music.
Added Partner Toons! They act like doodles and help you by attacking cogs with gags.
The Security Goon has been renamed to the 'Chief Security Goon'.
  His eye is now red. And it will turn purple when he enters phase 2.
More Battle Speeds have been added (From Endless, but added in a smaller amount)
Added 13 new items (All but one are shoes), 16 new achievements (Half involving Endless), and 3 Pocket Pranks.
Fixed a bug with the health colors
[TITLE] End Note
This may not be the perfect fork, but I hope I can at least leave the game on a high note. Cheers! <3"
metadata/_custom_type_script = "uid://d1j0hh6tsgy0r"
